            "Voice cloning configuration from VoxCPM Voice Cloning node. Provides voice_design, prompt_audio, reference_audio, trim_silence.": "来自 VoxCPM 语音克隆节点的语音克隆配置。提供：语音设计(voice_design)、情感参考音(prompt_audio)、音色参考音(reference_audio) 和 消除静音(trim_silence)。",
            "Advanced parameters from VoxCPM Advanced Parameters node. Provides min/max_tokens, temperature, sway, use_cfg_zero_star, retry_*.": "来自 VoxCPM“高级参数”节点的参数。提供:最大/小Token数 (min/max_tokens)、温度(temperature)、偏移(sway)、开启CFG零采样(use_cfg_zero_star) 以及重试(retry_*) 参数。"
        },
        "outputs": {
